
LCA Problem ----> find LCA in BST (easy)
            |
            ----> find LCA in BT  ----> has parent pointer (easy)
            |                     |
            |                     ----> no parent pointer (medium)
            |
            ----> find LCA in non-BT (hard)
            |
            |
            ----> Tarjan Algorithm: find LCA multiple times (off-line)
